and the UnSub knows that.

193
00:10:26.166 --> 00:10:28.500
Brian and Melissa Cain
were abducted on a Saturday night.

194
00:10:28.500 --> 00:10:29.834
Their last known credit card purchase

195
00:10:29.834 --> 00:10:32.000
