218
00:11:22.500 --> 00:11:24.917
It's dark. they're not paying attention.

219
00:11:24.917 --> 00:11:26.208
He jimmies a door.

220
00:11:26.208 --> 00:11:27.709
But that would leave a mark.

221
00:11:27.709 --> 00:11:29.208
He didn't leave any marks.

222
00:11:29.208 --> 00:11:32.166
All right. well.
let's go look at the other car.

223
00:11:39.709 --> 00:11:41.500
